OL,4,CA barber's journey converting to Islam
OL,6,FHe's been a barber since he was 16
OL,7,Fyears-old and has been building his
OL,8,Fown barber business since he was 19
OL,9,Fyears-old.
OL,11,F"My door to faith started through the
OL,12,Fbarber shop because the barber shop is
OL,13,Falways a place for men to come and
OL,14,Ftalk.
