OL,4,CA barber's journey converting to Islam
OL,6,FTom's quest has taken him to places
OL,7,Flike Egypt and the holy city of Mecca.
OL,8,FAlong the way, he's also taught
OL,9,Fhimself Arabic.
OL,11,F"Right now we're in the month of
OL,12,FRamadan so fasting is something I do
OL,13,Fand my brother also", said Tom.
OL,15,F"It's just about having that intention
OL,16,Fand the determination to know that
OL,17,Fyou're doing this for a higher
OL,18,Fpurpose."
