OL,3,C'It's such a beautiful way of life' -
OL,4,CA barber's journey converting to Islam
OL,6,FTom said he still has lots to learn
OL,7,Fabout the religion, but it's the
OL,8,Fbusiness he founded where he tries to
OL,9,Fput his values into practice each day.
OL,11,F"Something I really try to implement
OL,12,Fis just having a space where people
OL,13,Fcan talk." He said.
OL,15,F"I try to emphasise clean
OL,16,Fconversation, talking positively, not
OL,17,Fbringing each other down and having a
OL,18,Fnice, friendly environment for people
OL,19,Fto come to."
